title: Emma Pajak
text:
I am a PhD candidate at Imperial College London working in Optimisation and Machine Learning for Process Engineering (OptiML PSE) in the Department of Chemical Engineering supervised by Dr Antonio Del Rio Chanona.
I am conducting my studies as a student in the EPSRC Centre for Doctoral Training in Next Generation Synthesis & Reaction Technology (React CDT).
My research is focused on supply chain optimisation in collaboration with and funded by BASF.
